metadata.name: Antheia
metadata.description:
The goddess of flowers, blossoms, vegetation, and human love.

To dear my collectors, your support helps my inspiration to bloom and grow. I want to give you this piece as a token of appreciation. I hope you continue to follow and support my art journey. As I grow, our story also grows together. Thank you, fam.

Love,

Seungdo
